snippet.title: RTLOL x Avalanche Tournament Highlights
snippet.description:
In this compilation of highlights we present you with some of the best plays from top tier RTLOL players during the matches of our 10,000$ Avalanche sponsored Tournament!

Interested in playing in one of our upcoming events or hone your skills for the upcoming launch? Download the game for free via Elixir - https://launcher.elixir.app/games/raini-the-lords-of-light
